{"tid":177182,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人明皮膚差嘅人感受","createTime":"2017-03-28T16:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T16:49:11.000Z","uid":13031,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77eca69a35759240deeb196681892627482b7171","tid":177182,"uid":13031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:19:12.000Z","msg":"連望鏡都唔想<br />\n同人對望都唔敢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好羨慕皮膚好嘅人<br />\n無論我生活有幾健康 <br />\n煎炸嘢戒晒<br />\n日日運動同早瞓<br />\n做足護膚同facial<br />\n啲暗瘡同印永遠都唔會離開我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反<br />\n啲人唔運動又食煙<br />\n夜訓又食熱氣嘢<br />\n依然係皮膚好好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公平咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a17268a8d1a48bcb2e8c1941f09df17b8eb90c6","tid":177182,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:21:09.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8acf0c04777356b7edd26048b8f477e4fdb0c2","tid":177182,"uid":99476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:23:30.000Z","msg":"屌巴打我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f644dc789fa028c50b5e324adff422e7d7cc7fc","tid":177182,"uid":27998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":